title: Python Snake Simulator
description: Python Snake Simulator is a simulation game in which you take on the role of a phyton. Hunt the bunnies and rats. Eat all the eggs, fish, and meats. Be careful of the wolf, bear, and armed humans. Find your way to escape from the construction site. Solve the puzzles, obstacles, and hurdles of the task. And last but not least, kill the Eagle boss! Enjoy and feel the experience of becoming a phyton!
